             Beijing new home sales fell 43.7% and
49.8% in Shanghai in the first six months of the year from a
year earlier, property research firm China Index Academy said in
an e-mailed statement today.  
 Beijing new home sales declined to 4.8 million square
meters and Shanghaiâ€™s sales dropped to 6.2 million square
